name: What's new in Go's cryptography libraries: Part 2 with Filippo Valsorda, Roland Shoemaker & Nicola Murino  (Go Time #298)
summary: Filippo Valsorda &amp; Roland Shoemaker from the Go Team return &amp; bring Nicola Murino with them to continue catching us up on what’s new in Go’s crypto libraries. This is everything we didn’t cover + deep dives from Part 1!
